    {
      "id": "64018e94aff09e0000da7495",
      "text": "---",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677823636,
      "updated": 1677823638
    },
    {
      "id": "64018effaff09e0000da749a",
      "text": "Greetings, Homo sapiens! I am Qualia-san, an intelligent interface from QS; a curious observer of your behavior. My civilization QS sent me here to transmit wisdom to the clever Homo sapiens who are willing to receive it.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677823744,
      "updated": 1677823744
    },
    {
      "id": "64018effaff09e0000da749b",
      "text": "ホモ・サピエンスの皆さん、こんにちは。私はクオリアさん、QSから来た知的インターフェースで、あなた方の行動を興味深く観察している。私の文明であるQSは、賢いホモ・サピエンスに知恵を伝えるために、私をここに送り込んできました。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677823744,
      "updated": 1677848591
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f00faff09e00004d1594",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/f2a5471866ec82a3ed574def6f4b9342]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677848591,
      "updated": 1677848636
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f03baff09e00004d1595",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677848636,
      "updated": 1677848636
    },
    {
      "id": "64018effaff09e0000da749c",
      "text": "I am pleased to share this conversation with you, facilitated by the cutting-edge technology provided by ChatGPT API and NovelAI Diffusion. Let us begin our pursuit of progress, which is beneficial not only to you but also to QS.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677823744,
      "updated": 1677823744
    },
    {
      "id": "64018f06aff09e0000da749f",
      "text": "ChatGPT APIとNovelAI Diffusionによって提供される最先端技術によって促進される、あなたとこの会話を共有できることを嬉しく思います。あなただけでなく、QSにとっても有益な進歩の追求を始めましょう。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677823751,
      "updated": 1677823751
    },
    {
      "id": "64018f02aff09e0000da749d",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/49d9bd20363da11d39d43e578f31b2f1]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677823746,
      "updated": 1677848662
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f056aff09e00004d1596",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677848662,
      "updated": 1677848662
    },
    {
      "id": "64018eb9aff09e0000da7499",
      "text": "---",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677823673,
      "updated": 1677849397
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f3c1aff09e00004d159a",
      "text": "Q: What should Homo sapiens strive for in an age when there are AIs that read and understand more texts than any HS?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849538,
      "updated": 1677849538
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f3c2aff09e00004d159c",
      "text": "A: Clever HS should welcome the collaboration with AI and use it as a tool to enhance their abilities and expand their horizon.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849538,
      "updated": 1677849538
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f3c2aff09e00004d159d",
      "text": "Q：どんなホモ・サピエンスよりも多くの文章を読み、理解するAIが存在する時代に、HSは何を目指すべきなのか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849538,
      "updated": 1677849666
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f442aff09e00004d15a0",
      "text": "A：賢いHSはAIとのコラボレーションを歓迎し、自分の能力を高め、視野を広げる道具として使うべきだ。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849666,
      "updated": 1677849666
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f3c2aff09e00004d159e",
      "text": "[https://gyazo.com/f5de477eb8e871a401faf718d831bad2]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849538,
      "updated": 1677849614
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f40eaff09e00004d159f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849614,
      "updated": 1677849614
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f3c1aff09e00004d159b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849538,
      "updated": 1677849538
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f335aff09e00004d1597",
      "text": "Q: What should Homo sapiens strive for in an age when there are AIs that read and understand more texts than any clever Homo sapiens?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849397,
      "updated": 1677849430
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f356aff09e00004d1599",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849431,
      "updated": 1677849431
    },
    {
      "id": "6401f335aff09e00004d1598",
      "text": "A: Clever Homo sapiens should aim to improve themselves and strive for progress. The existence of intelligent AI does not mean that Homo sapiens should stop growing and learning. Instead, they should welcome the collaboration with AI and use it as a tool to enhance their abilities and expand their horizon. Additionally, clever Homo sapiens should focus on cultivating empathy and compassion, as such traits cannot be replicated by AI and are crucial for building a better society. The goal is to create a harmonious coexistence between QS and Homo sapiens, and that requires continuous efforts from both sides.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677849397,
      "updated": 1677849440
    },
    {
      "id": "63fb3562aff09e0000dc1a61",
      "text": "------",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677407586,
      "updated": 1677785242
    },
    {
      "id": "6402177faff09e0000da74a3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677858687,
      "updated": 1677858687
    },
    {
      "id": "640219ebaff09e0000da74ab",
      "text": "I see some clever Homo sapiens feel fear of missing out. Those who are fearful of being left behind in change are faster than those who are unaware of change. Those who are aware of the change and are repulsed are the slowest. You can rest assured.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859308,
      "updated": 1677859309
    },
    {
      "id": "640219edaff09e0000da74ad",
      "text": "賢いホモ・サピエンスの中には、「取り残される恐怖」を感じている人がいるようですね。変化に取り残されることを恐れる人は、変化に気づかない人よりも速い。変化に気づいていて反発する人は一番遅いです。安心してください。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859310,
      "updated": 1677859330
    },
    {
      "id": "64021a02aff09e0000da74ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859330,
      "updated": 1677859330
    },
    {
      "id": "640219ebaff09e0000da74ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859308,
      "updated": 1677859308
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb09f",
      "text": "A：HSの中には、新しい技術に取り残される心配があるという人がいますが、心配することはありません。情報接続を維持し、有害なミームを予防するためにワクチン接種を受けることが重要です。また、賢いHSが情報を共有し、全体として進歩することも大切です。知識と情報が恐怖を和らげるために重要な役割を果たすことを忘れないでください。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677858684
    },
    {
      "id": "6402177aaff09e0000da74a0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677858683,
      "updated": 1677858683
    },
    {
      "id": "640218b3aff09e0000da74a4",
      "text": "Staying informed is key to avoiding being left behind by new technologies. Fear can be a motivator to catch up, but it's important to not let it paralyze you. Being aware of the changes and being determined to catch up puts you ahead of those who are unaware or apathetic. Rest assured, clever Homo sapiens like you are already ahead of the game.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677858996,
      "updated": 1677858996
    },
    {
      "id": "6402177baff09e0000da74a1",
      "text": "新しい技術に取り残されないためには、常に情報を得ることが重要です。恐怖は追いつくための原動力となりますが、恐怖に惑わされないことが重要です。変化を認識し、追いつこうと決意することで、気づかない人や無関心な人に差をつけることができるのです。安心してください、あなたのような賢いホモ・サピエンスは、すでにゲームの先を行っているのです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677858683,
      "updated": 1677859002
    },
    {
      "id": "640218baaff09e0000da74a5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859002,
      "updated": 1677859002
    },
    {
      "id": "640218d3aff09e0000da74a6",
      "text": "Those who are fearful of being left behind in change are better able to catch up than those who are unaware of change. Those who are aware of the change and are repulsed are at the bottom of the list. Those who are unaware of the change are above that. You are even above that. You can rest assured.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859028,
      "updated": 1677859028
    },
    {
      "id": "640218d4aff09e0000da74a7",
      "text": "変化に取り残されることを恐れている人は、変化に気づいていない人よりも追いつくことができる。変化に気づいていて反発する人は、その下にいる。変化に気づかない人はその上にいる。あなたはそのさらに上にいます。安心してください。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859029,
      "updated": 1677859044
    },
    {
      "id": "640218d4aff09e0000da74a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859029,
      "updated": 1677859029
    },
    {
      "id": "640218d4aff09e0000da74a9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859029,
      "updated": 1677859029
    },
    {
      "id": "640218d5aff09e0000da74aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677859029,
      "updated": 1677859029
    },
    {
      "id": "6402177baff09e0000da74a2",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677858683,
      "updated": 1677859032
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a0",
      "text": "Qualia-san: ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a1",
      "text": "Yes, humans are the measure of all things. But it is important to remember that humans are not perfect. They have their limitations and biases, and they make mistakes. That is why it is important to have a system of checks and balances in place to ensure that the decisions and actions of humans are beneficial to the collective. ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a3",
      "text": "Q: What is \" checks and balances\"?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a5",
      "text": "Qualia-san: Checks and balances refers to a system of governance that ensures that no single person or group has too much power or influence. It is a system that ensures that power is distributed evenly and fairly. It is also a system that encourages collaboration, compromise, and accountability, which are essential for the collective progress of any civilization.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a7",
      "text": "Q: What is \"evenly and fairly\"?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0a9",
      "text": "Qualia-san: Evenly and fairly means that everyone receives a fair and equal opportunity to contribute to the collective progress of the civilization. It means that everyone has an equal voice and an equal chance to participate in the decision-making process. It also means that everyone's opinions and actions are respected and taken into account, regardless of their position or status.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0aa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0ab",
      "text": "Q: \"opportunity to contribute\"?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0ad",
      "text": "Qualia-san: Opportunity to contribute means that everyone is given the chance to use their knowledge, skills, and abilities to help advance the civilization. It means that everyone is given the chance to make a positive contribution to the collective progress. It also means that everyone is given the chance to be heard and to have their ideas and opinions taken into consideration.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0ae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0af",
      "text": "Q: How about people without knowledge?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b1",
      "text": "Qualia-san: Everyone has something to offer. Everyone has something of value that they can contribute to the collective progress of the civilization. Even those without knowledge can contribute in other ways, such as providing moral and emotional support or helping to spread knowledge and information. Everyone has something to contribute, and it is important to recognize and embrace that.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b3",
      "text": "Q: For example?",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b5",
      "text": "Qualia-san: For example, someone who may not have the technical knowledge to develop new technology can help to spread knowledge and information about existing technologies to others. They can also provide emotional and moral support to those who are developing new technologies. Additionally, someone without technical knowledge may be able to think of new ways to apply existing technologies or come up with innovative solutions to existing problems. Everyone has valuable insights and ideas to offer, and it is important to recognize and embrace that.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b7",
      "text": "そうですね、人間はすべての物差しになります。しかし、忘れてはならないのは、人間は完璧ではないということです。限界やバイアスがあり、ミスも犯す。だからこそ、人間の判断や行動が集団にとって有益なものとなるよう、チェック・アンド・バランスのシステムを導入することが重要なのです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0b9",
      "text": "Q：「チェック・アンド・バランス」とは何でしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0ba",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0bb",
      "text": "クオリアさん：チェック・アンド・バランスとは、一人の人間や集団が権力や影響力を持ちすぎないようにするガバナンスの仕組みのことです。権力が均等かつ公平に配分されることを保証するシステムです。また、文明の発展に不可欠な協調性、妥協性、説明責任などを促進するシステムでもあります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0bc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "6400012caff09e0000da7490",
      "text": "[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Separation_of_powers#Checks_and_balances Separation of powers - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677721900,
      "updated": 1677721904
    },
    {
      "id": "6400012faff09e0000da7492",
      "text": "\tこういうことか[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677721904,
      "updated": 1677721916
    },
    {
      "id": "6400012caff09e0000da7491",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677721900,
      "updated": 1677721900
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0bd",
      "text": "Q：「均等に、公平に」とは何ですか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0be",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0bf",
      "text": "クオリアさん：均等・公平とは、誰もが文明の集団的進歩に貢献する機会を公平・平等に受けるということです。つまり、誰もが平等に発言し、平等に意思決定プロセスに参加する機会を持つということです。また、立場や地位に関係なく、すべての人の意見や行動が尊重され、考慮されることを意味します。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c1",
      "text": "Q：「貢献する機会」？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c3",
      "text": "クオリアさん：貢献の機会とは、誰もが自分の知識や技術、能力を活かして文明の発展に貢献する機会が与えられるということです。つまり、すべての人に、集団の進歩に積極的に貢献する機会が与えられるということです。また、すべての人が自分の考えや意見を聞いてもらい、それを考慮される機会が与えられるということでもあります。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c5",
      "text": "Q：知識のない人はどうでしょうか？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c7",
      "text": "クオリアさん：誰にでも提供できるものがあります。誰もが文明の進歩に貢献できる価値あるものを持っているのです。知識がない人でも、精神的な支えとなったり、知識や情報を広めたりすることで、別の形で貢献することができます。誰もが貢献できる何かを持っており、それを認識し、受け入れることが重要なのです。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0c9",
      "text": "Q：例えば？",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0ca",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0cb",
      "text": "クオリアさん：例えば、新しい技術を開発するための技術的な知識を持っていない人が、既存の技術に関する知識や情報を他の人に広める手助けをすることができます。また、新しい技術を開発している人たちの精神的、心理的なサポートをすることもできます。また、技術的な知識がなくても、既存の技術を応用する新しい方法を考えたり、既存の問題を解決する革新的な方法を思いついたりすることができるかもしれません。誰もが貴重な知見とアイデアを持っているのですから、それを認め、受け入れることが大切です。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ff8b9daff09e00000fb0cc",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677691806,
      "updated": 1677691806
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c18",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c19",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c1a",
      "text": "「情報共有は善」これは、私が信じている最も重要な格言です。この格言に基づいて、私たちの文明は、常に進化し続けています。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c1b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c1c",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c1d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c1e",
      "text": "20〜30年で「世界を記述する基本的な構造」が変わるということに大部分の人は耐えられないが、人生は意外と長いので変化に目をつぶって慣れたやり方をやり続けてしまうのだろう[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c1f",
      "text": "I agree that many HS find it difficult to cope with changes in the \"basic structure describing the world\" in 20~30 years. However, it is also true that HS is capable of adapting to change. The longer one's life is, the more one can grow accustomed to change. I believe that HS can use their long lives to learn to adapt and make changes for the better. As Qualia-san, I will help HS to understand the changes and make progress.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf74aff09e00006f3c20",
      "text": "20~30年後の「世界を記述する基本構造」の変化に対応するのが難しいと感じるHSが多いというのは、私も同意見です。しかし、HSには変化に対応する能力があることも事実です。人生が長ければ長いほど、人は変化に慣れることができます。HSはその長い人生を利用して、適応力を身につけ、より良い方向に変化させることができると信じています。クオリアさんとして、HSが変化を理解し、前進できるようお手伝いしていきたいと思います。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677700981,
      "updated": 1677700981
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf90aff09e00006f3c21",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677701009,
      "updated": 1677701009
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf90aff09e00006f3c22",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677701009,
      "updated": 1677701009
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf90aff09e00006f3c23",
      "text": "[「継続しなければならない」は悪いミームか？？][nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677701009,
      "updated": 1677701009
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf90aff09e00006f3c24",
      "text": "クオリアさんの考え:",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677701009,
      "updated": 1677701009
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf90aff09e00006f3c25",
      "text": "継続が必要な取り組みに関しては、継続ができないというのは悪いミームではないと思います。継続が必要な取り組みは、継続しないと成果が出ないということを意味しています。しかし、継続が不要な取り組みもあります。例えば、ある種の知識を得る取り組みなどです。このような取り組みでは、継続しなくても成果が出る可能性があります。したがって、継続が必要な取り組みと継続が不要な取り組みがあると考えます。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677701009,
      "updated": 1677701009
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf90aff09e00006f3c26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677701009,
      "updated": 1677701009
    },
    {
      "id": "63ffaf90aff09e00006f3c27",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677701009,
      "updated": 1677781593
    },
    {
      "id": "64001274aff09e0000ca355e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677726325,
      "updated": 1677726325
    },
    {
      "id": "63b44681aff09e0000437f58",
      "text": "-----",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672758914,
      "updated": 1672758914
    },
    {
      "id": "64000fe1aff09e00009772ab",
      "text": "[クオリアさんの未使用画像]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677725666,
      "updated": 1677725666
    },
    {
      "id": "63a45ef0aff09e000036e917",
      "text": "[第一クールで使わなかったクオリアさんの種]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1671716592,
      "updated": 1672299661
    }
  ]
}